metadata.name: The ocean of life
metadata.description:
This ocean of peace and happiness
Where the treasures float now
From where I have been swimming for years
I dance life in harmony
Luminous and fresh
Like a new spring
Soothing and invigorating at the same time
Bursting with lime
With a touch of sunset
My deep and mysterious eyes
In my constructive goals
From where I know my limits
With this newfound serenity
Here I am


Edition 1/1 
2022.
